definitions.definition: The measurement of time , or determining what the local time is: the act or process of keeping the time .

subdefinitions.definition: Measuring and recording the time spent by employees on the clock , including the timepoints at which they clocked in and clocked out .

definitions.definition: The quality of being punctual, keeping to a set time.

main_definition: The measurement of time , or determining what the local time is: the act or process of keeping the time .
secondary_definitions: The quality of being punctual, keeping to a set time.
